{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_06_02",
  "title": "奥山すみれ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（誰か自主練しているみたいだな）\n（……この声は、すみれか）",
      "startTime": 3.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、なんか違うな……",
      "startTime": 8.9197081248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんがやると、もっとキリっとしてるのに……\n私がやっても、ただ背伸びしてるだけって感じ",
      "startTime": 17.5634582974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんっぽく言ってみようかな\nわ、「私達の歌で、胸躍らせよう」……！",
      "startTime": 25.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4725.422890900003,
          "startTime": 30.5920895576
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "きゃっ！？\n今の……瑠依ちゃんの真似、見てたんですか……？",
      "startTime": 32.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いや、たまたま通りかかってな……\n瑠依のストーカーは止めたんじゃなかったのか？",
      "startTime": 39.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "ストーカーはしてません、これはあくまで自主練です！",
      "startTime": 42.4952850341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなでレッスンした映像を見返してみたんですけど\nセンターに立っても、私いまいち地味で",
      "startTime": 51.4617029783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "なので、せめて瑠依ちゃんみたいな雰囲気だけでも\n身につけられればって、思ったんですけど……",
      "startTime": 59.9000017803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなと何かあったのか？",
      "startTime": 63.1351507027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "喧嘩したとか、そういう訳じゃないんです！\n練習でも仲良くやってる……と、思います",
      "startTime": 68.8000017803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、動きを合わせてみるとまだぎこちなくて\nミーティングもみんな遠慮し合ってる感じで",
      "startTime": 78.9000134786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "……合宿の時は、あんなに楽しかったのにな",
      "startTime": 82.6119716405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんなら、別のグループの子達と組んでも\n凄いステージに出来るんだろうなぁ……って",
      "startTime": 91.5387556478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（……これは、俺が言い方を間違えたかな？）\n（劣等感を持ってほしかった訳じゃないんだが……）",
      "startTime": 99.8666847229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依は確かに凄いけど、やり方は一つじゃない\nすみれにしか出来ないことだってあるだろう？",
      "startTime": 107.4666847229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "……そうなんでしょうか",
      "startTime": 110.110428675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺も一緒に考えるから、ちょっと一息入れようか\n今ならそこの自販機のおしるこ缶もついてくるぞ？",
      "startTime": 116.5666847229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "やったぁ！\n{user}さん、太っ腹ですね！",
      "startTime": 121.8333513896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 126.0221515178
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "ふう……",
      "startTime": 127.0721515178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（落ち込んでたの、少しは落ち着いたかな……？）",
      "startTime": 128.8753487865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "あっ……そこって確か、さとみさんの机ですよね？",
      "startTime": 132.5363905072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ、芽衣さんとすずちゃんがお菓子を\n食べた後かと思うくらいガチャガチャですね……",
      "startTime": 143.1333513896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さん、前はちゃんと片付けてたんだけどなぁ……\n忙しいと掃除を後回しにしたくなるのは分かるんだけど",
      "startTime": 152.3000160217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "確かにさとみさん、最近ちょっと変な感じです\n栄養ドリンクをガブ飲みしたり、塀の上に立ってたり",
      "startTime": 161.1000160217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "栄養ドリンクは分かるけど……なんで塀の上？",
      "startTime": 166.1454230269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……あ、分かりました！\n{user}さんは、なぜだと思います？",
      "startTime": 175.6739263795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "え、それクイズなのか！？　大人が塀の上に乗るなんて\nいや、俺はあまり人のことは言えないか……？",
      "startTime": 183.333349355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、正解です！",
      "startTime": 186.7380045374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "私、知ってるんですよ～\n塀の上で、芽衣さんとデートしてたって話",
      "startTime": 192.6333473205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは、こっちもいろいろあってというか\n結果的に芽衣も事務所入りしたからOKというか……！",
      "startTime": 200.2333473205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんが机を散らかしてるのも\n{user}さんが、そうしてるからなのかも",
      "startTime": 206.8000119526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr022.m4a",
      "text": "机を散らかしたままにしておくと\n凄いインスピレーションが湧いたりするんですか？",
      "startTime": 212.8000119526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr023.m4a",
      "text": "でも、たまにはちゃんと片付けないと\n沙季さんにまた怒られちゃいますよ",
      "startTime": 219.3000099181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "う……。き、気をつけるよ……",
      "startTime": 221.9589877883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr024.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんは……他には何をしてたっけ\n怜さんの後をつけたり、リズノワを盗撮したり……",
      "startTime": 230.8666765848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-smr025.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしてそれも\n{user}さんの真似だったんでしょうか",
      "startTime": 237.9637956658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "断じて俺は、やましいことはしてないからな！？",
      "startTime": 240.8853149055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
